claim.claim-text:
11. An ISBM beverage container comprising:
a propylene-based impact copolymer exhibiting a melt flow rate of from about 1 dg/min to about 150 dg/min.;
a maximum top load of at least about 160 N at a weight of 23 g;
a cold temperature drop impact resistance of at least about 6 feet; and
a haze of at least 10% as measured by a haze meter.
